reviewText: nephew loved it watches it all them time
Who doesn't love Sponge Bob! Bought it as a joke for a friend and he loved it! Lol
It was OK it don't play right but its ok
Lots of episodes for a very low price!  My son is very happy with this DVD and I will be purchasing the other similar ones as well.
3 DVDs for the price of one. You can't go wrong.
Thank you just what my son wanted contains 3 dvds from 2004 and 2005. Worth buying if your child or you likes spongebob

This will not disappoint any SpongeBob fan.  The episodes included on this disc are:

Disc 1:
SpongeBob B.C
Nature Pants
Fools in April
I'm With Stupid
Patty Hype
Squid on Strike
The Great Snail Race
Plankton's Army
Squilliam Returns
**Special Feature: Battle for Bikini Bottom PC Game Demo**

Disc 2:
Home Sweet Pineapple
Band Geeks
Sandy, SpongeBob & the Worm
Ripped Pants
Sandy's Rocket
Culture Shock
MuscleBob BuffPants
Employee of the Month
**Special Feature: Cast bios from the book SpongeBob Exposed! The Insider's Guide to SpongeBob SquarePants

Disc 3:
Have you Seen This Snail? (2 Part Episode)
The Lost Mattress
Krabs vs. Plankton
Good Neighbor
Skill Crane
The Great Snail Race
**Special Feature: Gary's Song" Karaoke

**I was sent this product in exchange for a honest review. The opinions above are my own.**
